### GET all posts

GET http://localhost:4000/posts

### Get a single post

GET http://localhost:4000/posts/1

### Create post

POST http://localhost:4000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title":"new post title"
}

### Update post

POST http://localhost:4000/posts/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title":"modified post title"
}

### Delete post

DELETE http://localhost:4000/posts/2